summary: Also I don't know whether I should ship those two or not I mean I don't wanna be the "friendship doesn't exist between two...
body:
Also I don’t know whether I should ship those two or not I mean I don’t wanna be the “friendship doesn’t exist between two characters” type of fangirl but somethings had me screaming!

Like when Crowley asked Aziraphale TWICE to run away together

Or when Aziraphale said to him “do something or I’m never gonna talk with you again” and Crowley immediately stopped time. Like,,the greatest threat to make him do something is to tell him Aziraphale isn’t gonna talk to him??,?

Or when Crowley thought Aziraphale was dead and somebody to love came on??

Or the way Aziraphale looked at Crowley in certain scenes.

I don’t know there’s just a lot of stuff.

Besides they’re an angel and a demon, they don’t actually have a gender, they’re beyond such petty things so,,,whatever
